To install the kinect and the needed simpleopenni libraries in processing follow this great tutorial here: http://code.google.com/p/simple-openni/wiki/Installation

The versions which worked on our systems perfectly were:
OpenNi 1.1.0.41 
NITE 1.3.1.3 
PrimeSensor 5.0.1.31 
PrimeSense Drivers 3.1.2.0

To setup processing and dynviz follow the SetupProcessingAndDynViz.doc included
